{"tid":1331921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自己老母自己救！即刻問下自己老豆老母聽日下畫去邊 唔好俾人捉左去遊行！","createTime":"2019-07-19T06:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T07:00:37.000Z","uid":280625,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc6802ab5ac2d6e0f9db0f6173ce1545f86b6ea","tid":1331921,"uid":280625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱啱我老母收到電話，有同鄉會啲朋友打嚟，話聽日一齊飲茶，之後一齊再去做義工﹙好似仲有講可能有啲車馬費﹚，我老母唔知頭唔知路就應承咗。<br />\n<br />\n之後我諗一諗，聽日？做義工？一定係捉你哋去遊行！<br />\n我老母話如果唔去唔係幾好，平時又同佢地去旅行、食好西，而家呢啲唔去會俾人講，我諗緊點捉佢留返喺度唔好出去！<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲問下自己老豆老母聽日會去邊！記得約佢地，或諗辦法留佢地係屋企，唔好俾佢地俾人捉左去撐警遊行！"},{"pid":"0ccfe3a59a3b705e969551219603f05fbd93af64","tid":1331921,"uid":2612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGEm7kx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGEm7kx.png&h=84eef868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VR1gWdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVR1gWdS.png&h=e9b1febb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4w4Y9yT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4w4Y9yT.png&h=5088c22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人話我知原來7月20取消左<br />\n<br />\nPrint 出黎痴係連儂牆比老人家知<br />\n<br />\nAirdrop 比人<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞到老人家白行一趟</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58e2815aeea096163c24c0249361e23817f5b78","tid":1331921,"uid":280625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"721 港島見"},{"pid":"d55a7ceabf292bd4496c5856dc8f13568f6f4703","tid":1331921,"uid":280625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"721 港島